channel.description:
hey i have my server source running and compiling but when i try to use the server no-ip its not letting others on my server.

does anyone know y?

item.title: I got a question on servers
item.dc:creator: @nov9862 nov9862
item.description:
@nov9862 wrote:

How The FUCK did you get repped?

Well back to my point. You need to portforward your router to allow people to gain access into your server. There are many tutorials on how to do this. Or www.portforward.com This Site will help, dont worry about choosing the right game to portforward just make sure you portforward 43594 or 5555.
